                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-230-off1347 t18261207-230-cd1348"></join>, 2 sixpences, 12 penny pieces,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182612070090"></xptr>15 half-pence, and 1 farthing, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18261207-230-victim1299" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Allibone
                     <interp inst="t18261207-230-victim1299" type="surname" value="Allibone"></interp>
